{"tid":863170,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【撻訂潮】上源驚現7連撻 殺定244.8萬","createTime":"2018-10-15T11:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T23:55:23.000Z","uid":174649,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3320991c66d6e467dddcb0ab8191498792ba13b2","tid":863170,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"樓市大吹淡風，新盤市場更驚現小規模撻定潮。萬科(香港)屯門掃管芴新盤上源，最新錄得7宗連環撻定，連同早前2伙撻定，項目本月累積撻定個案增至9伙，最新7伙，涉及總成交價4,897萬元，殺定金額料約244.8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n萬科本月1日國慶日首輪開賣上源347伙，首日全數單位沽清，惟該批單位先錄2宗撻定，隨著進行第二輪銷售，今日再增7宗撻定個案。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181015/large/1539596695_41fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181015%2Flarge%2F1539596695_41fb.jpg&h=ee20c23c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3583326f9340c0588c0f9ec5ae1e86ba9a64f9d8","tid":863170,"uid":120377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:40:20.000Z","msg":"活下去"},{"pid":"26dbf8fa94bf8f24782ae143ef98d9ad4cbd3a76","tid":863170,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:46:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c0da4c38661df9821f3ba96eccbe095832993bb","tid":863170,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"剛需呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6961b55ec7524df4ce119d4b1b5c3dad95fa1d73","tid":863170,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0da4c38661df9821f3ba96eccbe095832993bb","tid":863170,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:53:13.000Z","msg":"剛需呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"技術調整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0867cca2f36269d411687187a95119113e46c75b","tid":863170,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep